  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tbsp of coconut oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chicken to the saucepan and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced shallots and minced garlic to the saucepan and cook until softened, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add the sliced pickled ginger and Thai red curry paste to the saucepan and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the chicken broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Add the rice pilaf mix to the saucepan and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 10-12 minutes or until the liquid has been absorbed.",
    "Stir in the crumbled Stilton cheese until melted and well combined.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
